{"tid":1228093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"自由閪開始孤立自己","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T18:37:14.000Z","uid":207022,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68880391a7c88a968d36889e97424eb6ede73da0","tid":1228093,"uid":207022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"發夢經歷小弟係添華推進前線<br />\n而家心智真係會比幅圖講中哂<br />\n心情低落 想孤立自己 經常回起片段<br />\n仲記得當時前面有個女仔係前面個頭盔爆開<br />\n我沖上前禁住佢個頭走 希望佢無事<br />\n然後就開始後退 一路開槍<br />\n我日日都回常呢d畫面<br />\n星期一 可唔可以將責任交比大家 <br />\n希望用成功令我可以放鬆心入面舊大石<br />\n我知我係懦弱 各位可以話我搵藉口<br />\n但我都會同你地同一條船 共同進退<br />\n兄弟妹們祝凱旋歸來"},{"pid":"86c42a45518ad7dfb9b816b49404aabca8871849","tid":1228093,"uid":56063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"要睇住戰勝果一刻呀<br />\n過程係艱辛<br />\n但你不是一個人"},{"pid":"187a4745862513adb435413822f6fe0d486a1861","tid":1228093,"uid":78184,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"你並不孤單！<br />\n我們會一齊行落去，見證勝利的一刻！"},{"pid":"e9c505dcfe2fc9c1639d9c53ffb390ada95df8d0","tid":1228093,"uid":4730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bde4cdab39a899a16bf993ae5f49664c2678b19","tid":1228093,"uid":123562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"休息一下"},{"pid":"e1468dd40d70590d775543126c71ea62712fdc01","tid":1228093,"uid":149141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"可以 <br />\n每人都需要休息 一日唔夠就休兩日三日<br />\n留時間比自己差完電再返黎<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"f640a646a4470cde211b4dc72222ec264d713b86","tid":1228093,"uid":207470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:35:40.000Z","msg":"收到。"},{"pid":"74096eb73a627b3ca6806e6e06b7d0183096a114","tid":1228093,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:37:14.000Z","msg